COMPILATION:
premake4 gmake
make
./A2

INSTRUCTION:
- The implementation of viewport is based on constant window width and height.
  Resizing window will make viewport behave unusual.
- Changing viewport only appears when user drags a window. Clicking might result in disappearing or weird behaviour of the viewport.
  Please only drag to create new viewport.
- If you want viewport to fit the window after resizing, press A.
- Near plane is at 1.0
- Far plane is at 50.0

